Introduction

Nine is a South Korean singer under SXTYDGRS. She is a member of Kandis. She is also known for being a former contestant on the competitive survival show, K-pop Star 6: The Last Chance.

She appeared in JTBC's reality survival show, MIXNINE, as a trainee representing Mystic Entertainment auditioning to be a contestant. Unfortunately, she did not pass the auditions and hence did not become an official contestant on the show.
